(41, 1, 44, 40, 23, 2, 3, 'those things which Moses commanded', 'Authority of Moses'' Commands', 'This connection highlights the authority of Moses'' commands in both passages. Mark emphasizes following the Mosaic law for cleansing, while Matthew underscores the authority of the scribes and Pharisees who teach the law.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
