(41, 1, 45, 42, 5, 15, 17, NULL, 'Connection of Fame and Healing', 'Both passages emphasize the growing fame of Jesus, leading to large crowds seeking him for healing. Additionally, both accounts mention Jesus withdrawing to the wilderness, highlighting his need for solitude amidst the increasing demands of the people.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
